div.div:
The Yakmun clan, which boasted a long time ago, was wiped out in a massacre. The corpses piled up like mountains, and the blood flooded everything like ocean water. Amidst this hell of despair, Sura, opened his eyes: "No one shall be spared. I shall kill everyone. It doesn't end unless I've killed each and every one of them."
Jin Ja-Kang was the lone survivor, and with him a man's lonely revenge, which will be recorded as a legend in the Murimsa Temple in the future, begins!
(Source: KakaoPage, translated)

Dungeons and monsters suddenly appear and the world falls into chaos. Ki-Bong Kim, an ordinary young part-timer, has been sucked up into an awakening dimension for 3000 years to train his powers. When he makes his return to reality, he is a max-leveled player who only has one wish -- to reconcile with his loved ones. 10 years have passed in the real world during his absence. How will Ki-Bong be able to find his place in the world with his new limit-breaking abilities?
(Source: WEBTOONS, edited)
